description: This panel discussion features UNESCO Goodwill Ambassador Herbie Hancock and UNESCO Artist for Peace Marcus Miller. Organized by UNESCO and the Thelonious Monk Institute of Jazz, the 2014 International Jazz Day Daytime Educational Program took place at the Osaka School of Music in Osaka, Japan.
fulltitle: Intl Jazz Day 2014: Herbie Hancock & Marcus Miller: Artists for Peace and Cultural Diplomacy
